All team members must be students at an educational institution and <a
href="register_attend.php">registered paying Conference attendees</a> (Which
costs $20/person and covers all meals for the weekend, plus additional
exclusive MechMania-only food breaks.  Since online registration is now
closed, please e-mail <a
href="mailto:mechmania@acm.uiuc.edu">mechmania@acm.uiuc.edu</a> if you want
to participate in MechMania and are not yet registered as an attendee.). 
You will receive a confirmation e-mail from our staff after we process your
registration.

<p> If you have any questions or concerns, email <a href="mailto:mechmania@acm.uiuc.edu">mechmania@acm.uiuc.edu</a>.
